      "originalText": "Every 3 seconds:\n1. GET /metrics from each pod IP\n2. Parse kv_cache_usage_perc,\n   num_requests_waiting,\n   num_requests_running\n3. Compute weighted load score\n4. Store in Pod dataclass",
      "autoResize": true,
